The '''[[British Open]]''' is the Open Championship men's golf tournament.
'''British Open''' may also refer to: * [[Women's British Open]] of golf * [[The Championships, Wimbledon|The Wimbledon Championships]] of tennis * [[British Open Show Jumping Championships]] * [[British Open Squash Championships]] * [[British Open (snooker)]], a now defunct tournament * [[British Open Wheelchair Championships]], a wheelchair tennis tournament that is part of the ITF super series * [[BDO British Open]], one of the oldest competitive darts tournaments in the world * The dancing competitions of the [[Blackpool Dance Festival]]
